snippet.title: Champions of Middle-earth Trailer | Middle-earth: Shadow of War Mobile
snippet.description:
The Ring of Power calls to champions across Middle-earth. Unite to defeat Sauron's forces and fight for Mordor!

Join the fight. Pre-register today:
http://www.shadowofwar.com/mobile

—————

ABOUT THE GAME

Middle-earth: Shadow of War mobile is a free-to-play real-time RPG continuing Talion’s journey through Mordor. The game features iconic characters from Middle-earth: Shadow of Mordor and The Lord of the Rings trilogy, including Celebrimbor, Eltariel, Gimli, Boromir and many more fan-favorites.
